````` ::: ::: ## Stratified Logistic Reg ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} ordinal.mod1 <-glm(ssb_cat1~calfresh3 + Cohort + gender + race_eth + age + physical_activity + health_conscious + storage_access + units_four + paid_work_hours_tens + caregiving_hours_tens + homelessness_year, data = bns_combined_imputed_df, family = "binomial") ordinal.mod2 <-glm(ssb_cat2~calfresh3 + Cohort + gender + race_eth + age + physical_activity + health_conscious + storage_access + units_four + paid_work_hours_tens + caregiving_hours_tens + homelessness_year, data = bns_combined_imputed_df, family = "binomial") ordinal.mod3 <-glm(ssb_cat3~calfresh3 + Cohort + gender + race_eth + age + physical_activity + health_conscious + storage_access + units_four + paid_work_hours_tens + caregiving_hours_tens + homelessness_year, data = bns_combined_imputed_df, family = "binomial") ordinal.mod1 <- tidy(ordinal.mod1) %>% mutate(model = "Model 1") ordinal.mod2 <- tidy(ordinal.mod2) %>% mutate(model = "Model 2") ordinal.mod3 <- tidy(ordinal.mod3) %>% mutate(model = "Model 3") models <- bind_rows(ordinal.mod1, ordinal.mod2, ordinal.mod3) dwplot(models) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](Manuscript-Files_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-9-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: ## ````` ::: ::: ## Stratified Logistic Reg ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} imp_one_vs_zero <- with(bns_imputed_mids, glm(q77_one_vs_zero~calfresh3 + Cohort + gender + race_eth + age + health_conscious + cooking_confident + physical_activity + storage_room + food_insecure_2item, family = "binomial")) imp_one_vs_three_or_more <- with(bns_imputed_mids, glm(q77_one_vs_three_or_more~calfresh3 + Cohort + gender + race_eth + age + health_conscious + cooking_confident + physical_activity + storage_room + food_insecure_2item, family = "binomial")) ``` ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} imp_fv1_model_tidy <- pool(imp_one_vs_zero) |> summary() %>% mutate(model = "Odds of Eating 1-2 F&V Vs Zero", estimate = exp(estimate)) %>% select(-df) imp_fv2_model_tidy <- pool(imp_one_vs_three_or_more) |> summary() %>% mutate(model = "Odds of Eating 3 or More F&V Vs 1-2", estimate = exp(estimate)) %>% select(-df) FV2_models <- bind_rows(imp_fv1_model_tidy, imp_fv2_model_tidy) dwplot(FV2_models) + geom_vline(xintercept = 1, colour = "grey60", linetype = 2) + theme(legend.title = element_blank(), legend.position = c(0.8, 0.95), text = element_text(size = 10, face = "bold")) + xlab("Odds Ratio") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](Manuscript-Files_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-19-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: ##
